videos.description: Mason Plumlee forces a Nets turnover, then finds Jerami Grant on the break for a two-handed dunk.

videos.description: Kyrie Irving drives and uses a nice bounce pass to DeAndre Jordan, who rises up to stuff down a strong dunk for the Nets.
